<h1><a href="http://www.itinflections.com/dont-let-whaler-harpoon-companyor-career/" title="Link to Don’t Let a Whaler Harpoon Your Company…or Career">Don’t Let a Whaler Harpoon Your Company…or Career</a></h1>
        
<a class="fimage" href="http://www.itinflections.com/dont-let-whaler-harpoon-companyor-career/" title="Don’t Let a Whaler Harpoon Your Company…or Career"><img width="260" height="173" src="http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535-260x173.jpg" class="attachment-image-medium size-image-medium wp-post-image" alt="phishing" srcset="http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535-300x200.jpg 300w, http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535-543x362.jpg 543w, http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535-260x173.jpg 260w, http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535-125x83.jpg 125w, http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ThinkstockPhotos-487606535.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px" /> </a>
    <div>
        <div class="date">
        <ul>
            <li class="dated">September 28, 2016</li>
            <li class="email"><a href="http://www.itinflections.com/dont-let-whaler-harpoon-companyor-career/emailpopup/" onclick="email_popup(this.href); return false;"  title="Email This Post" rel="nofollow"><img class="WP-EmailIcon" src="http://www.itinflections.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-email/images/email_famfamfam.png" alt="Email This Post" title="Email This Post" style="border: 0px;" /></a>
